languages.text: "Спесивый нелюдь слышит слова, но не видит клинка, что за ним таится. Хорошо. Неосторожный и самоуверенный враг — неопасный враг".

traits.locale_text: "Спесивый нелюдь слышит слова, но не видит клинка, что за ним таится. Хорошо. Неосторожный и самоуверенный враг — неопасный враг".

languages.text: "The proud xenos hears the words but does not see the blade that stands behind them. Good. An enemy who is careless and overconfident is an enemy that poses little threat."

languages.text: «La orgullosa xenos oye lo que digo pero no ve la espada que se alza detrás. Eso está bien. Un enemigo descuidado y demasiado confiado presenta poca amenaza».

languages.text: 「誇り高き異種族は、その言葉を聞いても、その背後にある刃を見ない。いいことだ。油断をしている自信過剰な敵は脅威とならない」
languages.original_text: "The proud xenos hears the words but does not see the blade that stands behind them. Good. An enemy who is careless and overconfident is an enemy that poses little threat."

languages.text: “傲慢的异形听到了话语，却没有留意到身后的利刃。这很好，粗心大意、过于自大的敌人构不成什么威胁。”
languages.original_text: "The proud xenos hears the words but does not see the blade that stands behind them. Good. An enemy who is careless and overconfident is an enemy that poses little threat."

traits.locale_text: “傲慢的异形听到了话语，却没有留意到身后的利刃。这很好，粗心大意、过于自大的敌人构不成什么威胁。”

languages.text: "Die stolze Xenos hört die Worte, sieht die Klinge aber nicht, die hinter ihnen steht. Gut. Ein sorgloser und übermütiger Feind stellt nur eine geringe Gefahr dar."
languages.original_text: "The proud xenos hears the words but does not see the blade that stands behind them. Good. An enemy who is careless and overconfident is an enemy that poses little threat."

languages.text: « L'arrogante xénos entend les mots, mais ne perçoit pas la lame qui se dresse derrière eux. Tant mieux. Un ennemi confiant et imprudent est un ennemi qui ne représente aucune menace. »

languages.text: "Kibirli zenolar sözleri işitiyorlar ancak arkalarında duran kılıcı görmüyorlar. Güzel. Dikkatsiz ve kendine aşırı güvenen bir düşman, ciddi bir tehdit teşkil etmez."
